**Context**
spring-ai.version is 0.8.1

Could the pinecone add the configuration distance-type as [Neo4jVectorStore properties](https://docs.spring.io/spring-ai/reference/1.0-SNAPSHOT/api/vectordbs/neo4j.html#_neo4jvectorstore_properties) to allow custom distance metric? 

Thanks!

